data.description: Sellers contributing up to $5000 towards closing costs. The lender is also offering up to $5000 and a free appraisal when using the preferred lender.. Spectacular 5-bedroom,3-bathroom single-family home in an ideal location on a quiet street!  This property is conveniently situated near Turnpike on-ramps and US1,providing easy access to any destination.The home features vaulted ceilings and ceiling fans in all bedrooms. Additionally, there is a bedroom and full bathroom on the first floor. The HOA fees are low, and the property boasts a spacious 2-car garage with a paver driveway.For all financed offers, please include a DU report. Cash offers must provide proof of funds. It is important to note that this community does not have a CDD.
